{"tid":1419046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"監警會澄清：從未派遣任何觀察員履行職務","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:08:05.000Z","uid":169676,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"97889a3e5c9bc2acc8049fe812a9aa303aaac15c","tid":1419046,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:16:51.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】觀察員林浩揚上環被捕 監警會「割席」稱無派員觀察<br />\r\n<br />\r\n獨立監察警方處理投訴委員會（監警會）公佈，該會方一名並非委員會委員的觀察員，於昨日被警方拘留，監警會已獲警方證實事件。據民主黨黃碧雲透露，涉事被拘留的觀察員為民主黨黨員林浩揚，昨晚他在上環被捕。<span style=\"color: red;\">但監警會澄清，該會未於昨日派遣任何觀察員履行職務，故該人士被警方拘留原因，與監警會工作無關。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n監警會稱，在觀察員計劃下，保安局局長會委任合適人士出任監警會觀察員，並根據《監警會條例》第37條(1)(a)及(b)賦予的權力，觀察員負責協助監警會進行以下工作，包括出席警察課就某須匯報投訴而進行的會面及觀察投訴警察課在某須匯報投訴的調查中的證據收集。根據監警會網頁，該會共有109名觀察員。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190805/59899989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190805%2F59899989&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKT1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=dc5fb672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190805%2F59899989&h=329c7cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190805/59899989</a>"},{"pid":"8625cdef261bb637e71ebb3e7757ab64ad12e117","tid":1419046,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a289885397b03ad5e57fedefe3fc6748452241","tid":1419046,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8625cdef261bb637e71ebb3e7757ab64ad12e117","tid":1419046,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=